CPSU  can refer to:
* Central Philippines State University, a state university in the Philippines
* Communist Party of the Soviet Union
* Communist Party of the Soviet Union (1992)
* Communist Party of the Soviet Union (Shenin)
* Union of Communist Parties — Communist Party of the Soviet Union
* Communist Party of Social Justice — political party in Russia established in 2012
* Civil and Public Services Union - an Irish trade union
* Community and Public Sector Union - an Australian trade union
* California Polytechnic State University in San Luis Obispo, California, USA
* Commonwealth Policy Studies Unit
* Coventry Polytechnic Students Union
